# --- WIP exploration scripts: a leading _ means local-only, never committed ---
# Promote a script by renaming it (drop the _), then commit it and link it from
# a doc in the same change. Docs/claims cite only committed (no-_) scripts; a
# load-bearing verifier's evidence is ported to a C# witness, not committed as a
# script. Scoped to top-level: framework/ uses _ for legit private modules, and
# results/ + subdirs are intentionally left untouched.
simulations/_*.py
!simulations/__*.py

# --- Secrets / API keys (NEVER commit) ---
.env
.env.*
apikey.json
api_key.json
*.token
secrets.json
credentials.json
